==Non-diagonal tracks==
In OpenTTD there can be only one type of railtrack on each tile (except the [[en/Manual/Base Set/Railways|normal railway]] and [[en/Manual/Base Set/Electrified railways|electrified railway]]) so it is possible that you have to rebuild your railways first if you would like to mix the type of your close non-diagonal railway lines.
